---
layout: default
---

<section class="p-4 pt-12 bg-orange/10 grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 sm:h-[80vh]">
  <div class="col-span-2">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">The Globe Church is all about Jesus, made up of all sorts of people, involved in the greatest mission…</h1>
    <p>We’re a group of Christians gathering from across London near London Bridge.</p>
    <p>
      <a href="/sundays" class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-orange text-white no-underline transition-colors hover:bg-blue">Join us this Sunday</a>
      <a href="/about">Find out more about the church</a>
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    Hello world
  </div>
</section>

<div class="p-4">
<section class="p-4 border border-orange mb-4">
  <h2>Sunday Services</h2>
  <p>The Globe Church meets at 4pm every Sunday at Globe Ark Accademy. It's a few minutes walk from Elephant and Castle Tube station.</p>
  <a href="/sundays" class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-orange text-white no-underline transition-colors hover:bg-blue">Join us this Sunday</a>
  <a href="https://goo.gl/maps/ZYWE7cPGxr9NWBB1A" target="_blank" rel="noopener">See a map</a>
</section>

<section class="mb-4">
  <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b p-2 gap-4">
    <h2 class="font-bold text-lg uppercase">Upcoming events</h2>
    <a href="/calendar" class="">See the church calendar</a>
  </div>

  <div class="flex justify-between items-center p-2 gap-4">
    {% set oneOffEvents = events | eventsFuture | eventsOneOff | eventsSort %}
    <a href="/calendar/{{ oneOffEvents[0].startDate | formatDate }}/{{ oneOffEvents[0].slug }}/" class="w-full group no-underline transition-colors">
      IMG…
      <div class="bg-orange/10 p-4">
        {{ oneOffEvents[0].startDate | formatDate('dddd, D MMMM YYYY') }}<br />
        <strong class="block">{{ oneOffEvents[0].title }}</strong>
        <button class="rounded px-2 py-1 bg-orange text-white group-hover:bg-blue group-hover:text-white">More information</button>

      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/calendar/{{ oneOffEvents[1].startDate | formatDate }}/{{ oneOffEvents[1].slug }}/" class="w-full group no-underline transition-colors">
      IMG…
      <div class="bg-orange/10 p-4">
        {{ oneOffEvents[1].startDate | formatDate('dddd, D MMMM YYYY') }}<br />
        <strong class="block">{{ oneOffEvents[1].title }}</strong>
        <button class="rounded px-2 py-1 bg-orange text-white group-hover:bg-blue group-hover:text-white">More information</button>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="p-4 border border-orange mb-4">
  {% set sermon = preaching[0] %}
  <h2>Listen back to the latest sermon</h2>
  <p>{{ sermon.title.rendered }}</p>
  <a href="/resources/{{ sermon.slug }}" class="px-2 py-1 rounded bg-orange text-white no-underline transition-colors hover:bg-blue">Go to the recording</a>
</section>
</div>
